      "summary": {
        "zh-TW": "負責醫療資訊系統（HIS）前端開發與功能優化，涵蓋門診掛號、報到、看診流程與醫療表單管理，並配合院內流程進行客製化 UI/UX 與邏輯實作。",
        "en-US": "Developed and optimized a healthcare HIS frontend covering registration, check-in, clinical workflows, and complex form modules with customized UI/UX and business logic."
      },
      "highlights": [
        {
          "zh-TW": "串接健保卡讀卡機：處理讀寫卡流程、資料解析與錯誤防呆，確保前端流程與硬體穩定整合",
          "en-US": "Integrated NHI card reader: implemented read/write flow, parsing, and robust error handling"
        },
        {
          "zh-TW": "實作看診狀態控管與資格審核：依身分與就醫類型動態調整流程與畫面呈現，降低誤操作",
          "en-US": "Built visit-state control and eligibility checks with dynamic UI/flow by identity and visit type"
        },
        {
          "zh-TW": "重構 Vue/Quasar 元件與表單：降低重複邏輯、提升可維護性，並改善大型表單渲染與表格操作體驗",
          "en-US": "Refactored Vue/Quasar components and complex forms to reduce duplication and improve UX/performance"
        },
        {
          "zh-TW": "優化 API 呼叫流程：避免重複請求造成效能下降，並改善資料處理方式",
          "en-US": "Optimized API calling patterns to prevent duplicate requests and improve data handling"
        }
